modName: Breeze home - Extra rooms - part III - complete edition
summary: adds two new wings to the player home, breeze home!
descriptionHtml:
this mod, a compilation of both my other mods adds two brand new wings to breeze home.

-the first adds an armory on the second floor and a crafting room on the first floor
- the second moves to cooking pot and fire pot to a new room and adds a balcony to the second floor

to install the mod just make sure all esp\'s are activated in the data files at the same time, if not it will not work properly.

if you encounter any problems please contact me.
author: Wizzyboi
